   </Row>
   <Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0">
    <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">loc_15373294129891632404</Data></Cell>
    <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">[DEPRECATED] Get item or blueprint to fix Neuromod insertion chair. (this is to get player to head to another location so Igwe can retrieve body otherwise player can go straight to chair and wait.)</Data></Cell>
    <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">[DEPRECATED] หาไอเทมหรือพิมพ์เขียวเพื่อซ่อมเก้าอี้ติดตั้ง Neuromod</Data></Cell>
    <Cell><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
